

[Version]
$ openssl version

[Create RSA Private Key]
$ openssl genrsa -out FILE_NAME.key 2048    
EG: openssl genrsa -out private.key 2048

[Create new Private Key and CSR]
$ openssl req -nodes -newkey rsa:2048 -keyout FILE_NAME.key -out FILE_NAME.csr
EG: openssl req -nodes -newkey rsa:2048 -keyout custom.key -out custom.csr
